{
  "stem": "24346.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, yes, well, I missed-- in 1952, my other daughter-- I'm sorry, I missed it, because it happens, you can't remember everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So our daughter, second daughter, was born on January 30, 1952, in downtown New York, where we lived in that place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was born in Bellevue Hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think she was the only quite blonde baby in the world, there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they came in, that's all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was our other daughter, Sandy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what was the name of your business that you-- your business, what was it--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, it was Brook Boneless.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then came in the Wholesome Meat Act, a new law the Department of Agriculture passed that every place, it's got to be federal inspected.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were, in the first business we bought, we were state inspected, New York State.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we couldn't ship meats interstate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had only to sell the state of New York.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they came out, the Wholesome Meat Act in-- that was either 1969 or 1968, and they said everybody has to convert federal inspection, meaning you will be able to sell all over the country, to every state, even out of the country, to foreign countries.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We merged our firm, this Brook Boneless, merged with two other firms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was another firm, Ace Beef, and one, Ajax Packing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to do business before amongst each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, a father of these people that we ordered, he used to come to our place and saw how we, the newcomers, work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said-- and these were American people-- he said Bernie, the father said to one, join with these guys.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're good workers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They work hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're honest.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Merge with them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You'll be successful.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
